{"tid":2392672,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今次GME事件根本係上演緊一場「人性遊戲」","createTime":"2021-02-03T02:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T03:45:42.000Z","uid":19970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aa235e7fc5755169ab0da0a8e65482ed9738e593","tid":2392672,"uid":19970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:56:07.000Z","msg":"遊戲內容：<br />\n<br />\n1. 十個人，每人眼前有兩個掣，一紅一綠，每人開頭有$100000<br />\n<br />\n2. 遊戲會進行十Round，只要十Round都全員撳綠掣每人就+$100000，happy ending<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果每round有其中一個人撳紅色掣，果個人果round會+$50000，但其他人會-$20000<br />\n<br />\n4. 如果有一Round全部人撳紅掣，全員餘額歸零<br />\n<br />\n5. 每Round 之間大家可以溝通同討論<br />\n<br />\n6. 冇人知你每Round實際撳咩掣<br />\n<br />\n7. 十round後先會公布大家餘額有幾多，冇晒餘額嘅玩家就會死！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你會做自私果個定乖乖撳綠掣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114d9564b7536aa02f7e1c1ee5d12d9a48d1f09d","tid":2392672,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:58:48.000Z","msg":"你個例子無反映果種可以睇住大戶含撚既樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da408e6432f145f278dfa7b4ba8d7e13ef2cd4b5","tid":2392672,"uid":68097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:00:39.000Z","msg":"呢十個人, 本身有九個已經係大戶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1162cb1063ee747aee5df90695aa067ab950998","tid":2392672,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:01:49.000Z","msg":"<del>每人開頭有$100000</del><br />\n每人開頭要拎$100000出嚟"},{"pid":"2cd9fb9c07121b4a185253a6ab8b175115566c54","tid":2392672,"uid":37719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"真正好睇既係賦予左一個正義既原因黎令佢地甘心輸盡，同埋大大小小控制群眾心理既說辭"},{"pid":"4506bf2462ae20eacdbe39d65d9e85309e0c5f12","tid":2392672,"uid":229019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:45:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}